      "score": 5,
      "comments": 3,
      "author": "brn",
      "published": "2026-07-17T06:01:54Z",
      "bullets": [
        "PACT allows websites to cryptographically verify user attributes, such as active subscriptions, without tracking identities or sessions across the web.",
        "The protocol leverages blind signatures and zero-knowledge proofs to decouple credential issuance from presentation, preventing cross-site correlation.",
        "It aims to replace invasive tracking mechanisms for authentication and anti-bot checks with a standardized, privacy-preserving web credential API."
      ]
